opinion.case_name: In Re Discipline of Ashiru No. D-2410

opinion:
543 U.S. 1141

IN RE DISCIPLINE OF ASHIRU
No. D-2410.

Supreme Court of United States.

February 22, 2005.

1

Rahman Olalekan Ashiru, of Houston, Tex., is suspended from the practice of law in this Court, and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
